      • getPredicatesBetweenQA

        public static ListQueryAdapter<org.openrdf.model.URI> getPredicatesBetweenQA(org.openrdf.model.URI subjectNodeType,
                                                                             org.openrdf.model.URI objectNodeType,
                                                                             IEngine engine)
        Derives a query adapter capable of pulling out the predicates that connect all subject nodes of a given type and all object nodes of a given type. The results will contain *all* types, so they will generally be run through getTopLevelRelations(java.util.Collection, com.ostrichemulators.semtool.rdf.engine.api.IEngine) to get only the top-level relationships
        Parameters:
        subjectNodeType - The type (in URI form) of the subject node
        objectNodeType - The type (in URI form) of the object node
        engine -
        Returns:
        A proper query adapter capable of querying a knowledgebase for the desired predicates

      • getTopLevelRelations

        @Deprecated
public static Set<org.openrdf.model.URI> getTopLevelRelations(Collection<org.openrdf.model.URI> rels,

        Deprecated. use StructureManager.getTopLevelRelations(java.util.Collection)

        Parameters:
